;;; unindentation (single target)

;; high level steps to unindent a single item
;;
;; Assume an abstract tree thing like this:
;; - 0.
;; - 1.
;;   - 1.0.
;;   - 1.1.
;;     - 1.1.0.
;;   - 1.2.
;; - 2.
;; 
;; We want to unindent 1.1. First, indent everything after 1.1 (in this case
